// Ice Barrier — Mage stance-swap buff (Phase 4). Applied to the caster when entering Ice form
// (Fire -> Ice). Mechanics.md describes a true absorb shield ("gain ice barrier absorbing the
// next attack / projectile"); the real absorb system is deferred (see architecture §8.5), so the
// focused slice models it as a temporary damage-reduction buff (damage_taken_mult 0.6 = -40%
// incoming) through the existing status system — the same mechanism frostbite uses to amplify.
(
    id: "ice_barrier",
    display_name: "Ice Barrier",
    stacking: RefreshOnReapply,
    base_duration_secs: 3.0,
    damage_taken_mult: 0.6,
)
